{"tid":622895,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家有無諗過港珠澳大橋人工島防波堤係按照諸葛亮嘅八陣圖黎擺?","createTime":"2018-04-09T13:46:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-09T14:29:12.000Z","uid":96512,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8e492f583b27c4151354c37e6e1742e4f739e56a","tid":622895,"uid":96512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T13:46:12.000Z","msg":"相信大家都聽過諸葛亮嘅八陣圖有幾勁<br />\n內地百度有咁既說法<br />\n八陣圖傳說是由三國時諸葛亮創設的一種陣法。相傳諸葛亮御敵時以亂石堆成石陣，按遁甲分成「生、傷、休、杜、景、死、驚、開」八門，變化萬端，可擋十萬精兵。<br />\n<br />\n就連杜甫都寫左首&lt;&lt;八陣圖&gt;&gt;去歌頌諸葛亮有幾勁<br />\n正所謂:<br />\n「功蓋三分國，名成八陣圖，<br />\n江流石不轉，遺恨失吞吳」<br />\n<br />\n我絕對有理由相信中國已經搵返失傳已久嘅八陣圖<br />\n仲靈活運係防波堤之上<br />\n<br />\n孔子同耶穌都有講過:「兵如流水」<br />\n既然八陣圖可以擋得住千軍萬馬,自然都可以擋到<br />\n洶湧嘅海浪。所以防波堤個亂石陣係有用嘅,<br />\n我地要對偉大嘅祖國有信心<br />\n<br />\n不服來辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n申利:我唔會特登去試行條橋"},{"pid":"2ebe0632404500b05b46cf54925bfce671f76228","tid":622895,"uid":96512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T14:00:09.000Z","msg":"放返張中國特色嘅八陣圖先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/190337_a5f8d158822c02282101daab739ae865.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F190337_a5f8d158822c02282101daab739ae865.jpg&h=29508a2c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e043878eeedcf1e756a3eb4851bd4f579b0ac686","tid":622895,"uid":96512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T14:29:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180409/s00001/a1e318a3c439c643df7f38d0b00cbc88.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180409%2Fs00001%2Fa1e318a3c439c643df7f38d0b00cbc88.jpg&h=b5